"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/872671","Women and Equalities","false","2018-04-16","<p>Neither my Right Honourable Friend, nor any of her recent predecessors have had meetings with the SCL Group or Cambridge Analytica in their role as Minister for Women and Equalities.</p>","Louth and Horncastle","Victoria Atkins",,"2018-04-16T16:38:21.45Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/872671/answer","Biography information for Victoria Atkins","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/872671/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/872671/answer",,,,,"31","Women and Equalities","Women and Equalities","2018-03-27","Government Equalities Office: Cambridge Analytica​ and SCL Group","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for Women and Equalities, whether she or her predecessors met with representatives of the SCL group or Cambridge Analytica.","false","Biography information for Neil Gray","Airdrie and Shotts","Neil Gray","134485"
